description: Parking Cookie lets you easily record where you parked for future reference. Unlike other GPS-based parking utilities that don't work in garages or when satellites are unavailable, this utility is based on free-form text input. Examples of this include: "Term A Level 5 Pole C3", "West Lot 4A", "720 Main St St Paul MN", and "37.76 -122.40". The Map It button will launch Google Maps with the entered location as input, so that any address or GPS-based location will be mapped.
